s://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"e5c0576400e6169cd93ca3d9f99572a202cead41","tid":1667271,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13e71860fab006c6739fe1d50a1d1b591dc0d3ea","tid":1667271,"uid":247878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:55:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5b60aea46cd6a6d953d208618028792873cc3edd","tid":1667271,"uid":32278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"推"}]}